{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":610942,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":126712,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"现在进清华的中产以下的有多少呢","timestamp":1606277705,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":610958,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":126712,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"清华北大在国外基本就是富人子弟能进的学校？呃你如果是指国外的顶级私立大学，可能是这样，但如果从绝对实力的角度说，像ucb之类的公立学校比清北强多了，然而也并不是当地富人才能进的大学…","timestamp":1606277853,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":610997,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":126712,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"正是因为固化才会卷","timestamp":1606278345,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":610999,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":126712,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有合理的分配机制会有无效竞争吗？","timestamp":1606278373,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":611008,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":126712,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"本末倒置","timestamp":1606278430,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":611324,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":126712,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 90%以上","timestamp":1606281761,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":611332,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":126712,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 我这里的中产定义是有一百万以上闲钱的","timestamp":1606281877,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":126712,"reply":7,"tag":null,"text":"个人感觉，现在大学中普遍存在的焦虑和内卷其实是好事。本质上这种现象出现说明我国阶层从教育上，经济上还没有完全固化。还有想当一部分寒门学子能靠当下招生制度进入清华北大这类在国外基本就是富人子弟才能进入的学校。同样毕业生也能靠“内卷”“下死功夫”等方式实现经济阶层的改变。假若未来我国社会阶层进一步固化，进入清华北大的基本都是各省高收入中产家庭子女甚至富二代官二代那么内卷自然就不存在了，我们也可以像欧美那样大学搞真正的素质教育，但是那样真的就好吗？","timestamp":1606277383,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782655,"url":"","vote":{}}}